            "kind": "plain",
            "text": "إِنَّ الْقَوْمَ لَمْ يَجْرُوا فِي"
          }
        ]
      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:472:2",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/455/576",
      "text": [
        " حَلبةٍ تُعْرَفُ الْغَايَةُ عِنْدَ قَصَبَتِهَا فَإِنْ كَانَ وَلَا بُدَّ فَالْمَلِكُ الضِّلِّيلُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "The whole group of them did not proceed on the same lines in such a way that we can know the height of their glory; but if it has to be done then it is the “al-Mālik aḍ-ḍillīl” (the mislead king)."
        ]
      }
    },
